ygData.messageBody:
Hi, Lyssra's Darkwood Picaro (I believe is proper name) dropped off of the
1st Cazic Thule dispatched on Tribunal last night. Being the only Bard part
of the raiding party, I received this instrument with no contest. It appears
to be a flute by picture, I however, cannot find any information regarding
this items and any effects it may have. I cannot think of any way to test
any possible increased effect, due to the fact that it is a wind instrument.
Does anyone have any knowledge of this item, or know of a way that I might
test any effects it may have? Thanks.

Downs DePunisher
50 Wood Elf Bard
The Elitists, Tribunal
